cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use trainall in your research or product, please cite it."
title: "trainall: one library for the frontier LLM training stack"
abstract: >-
  trainall packages the modern LLM training stack — pre-training, CPT/DAPT, SFT,
  preference optimization (DPO/IPO/KTO/ORPO/SimPO/CPO), RLHF, RLVR+GRPO, agentic
  RL, distillation, self-play and LoRA/QLoRA — behind one config-driven,
  registry-based API.
type: software
